{"tid":630081,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"舉報fnn #5726 分身係五十肩 #10242 五十堅 #151409","createTime":"2018-04-15T09:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T14:26:10.000Z","uid":138981,"like":25,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf51f4c0348d586eb01e0fff3f2de95f11b0d1e","tid":630081,"uid":138981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舉報分身 <br />\n<br />\nfnn #5726<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/profile/5726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/profile/5726</a><br />\n<br />\n五十肩 #10242<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/profile/10242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/profile/10242</a><br />\n<br />\n五十堅 #151409<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/profile/151409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/profile/151409</a><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nAdmin你上次已經確認BAN咗我剛交了朋友 #57367 及 六根清淨 #8964<br />\n請調查fnn #5726，五十肩 #10242，五十堅 #151409是否分身被BAN<br />\n<br />\n而且五十肩 #10242 同 五十堅 #151409貼出自稱偷拍床照裸照已經犯LIHKG使用條款<br />\n(n). 於貼文內直接張貼成人圖片或影片<br />\n(b). 以任何方式傷害未成年人<br />\n(a). 上載、張貼、發送電子郵件或傳送任何非法、有害、脅迫、濫用、騷擾、侵害、中傷、粗俗、猥褻、誹謗、或道德上令人不快的「內容」。"},{"pid":"ab632b1143e5992b1dd7365a9a386c2413b44598","tid":630081,"uid":138981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>fnn 已有CC POST手足指出食過返見過fnn同五十肩為同一人</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/024014_16009d270670a26f2a62700eefa49824.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F024014_16009d270670a26f2a62700eefa49824.png&h=cb587d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五十肩另一連登分身 同舊登一樣叫fnn<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/5726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/5726</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/135217_ccc1236288caf8556ca422c19d7d326f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F135217_ccc1236288caf8556ca422c19d7d326f.png&h=79a2a678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">fnn=五十肩又再次自爆1994年出世</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/140025_5195ec1b8a50c005e6309538acb667a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F140025_5195ec1b8a50c005e6309538acb667a4.png&h=b250b6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五十肩舊登叫&rdquo;改名都咁拎煩&rdquo;/&ldquo;改名都咁撚煩&rdquo;/&ldquo;fnn&rdquo; </span></span></ins></strong><br />\n舊登ac: <a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=200481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2FProfilePage.aspx%3Fuserid%3D200481&d=9VWw9RWi4seHeKcNjBQbi%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dd2a4abb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=200481</a><br />\n<br />\n蠢到放<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">真名</span></strong>line ID上高登<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/230853_fb959c2d67b1841deea6c7c7c7b3e9a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F230853_fb959c2d67b1841deea6c7c7c7b3e9a5.png&h=6b1226dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">肩狗2011年(17歲)喺舊登自爆跟人組團北上叫雞</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/134637_5831ff9e8add39e474ba5d47451e1b65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F134637_5831ff9e8add39e474ba5d47451e1b65.png&h=0ab376ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/134638_9ad40a1207b1ea6e42cf17d8cfee6220.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F134638_9ad40a1207b1ea6e42cf17d8cfee6220.png&h=ba27d00e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/134657_5372f6cd06f9e6e1fb4ca1ad95b1a100.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F134657_5372f6cd06f9e6e1fb4ca1ad95b1a100.png&h=0725324b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街五十肩用高登fnn同連登ac貼同一個女友/ex圖<br />\n<br />\n上圖為高登fnn 下圖為連登五十肩</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/042546_7de7b6c790349ebcc17f01adc7f0ec0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F042546_7de7b6c790349ebcc17f01adc7f0ec0b.png&h=d04fca06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/042546_39b9aaed43cdd2a1769203f852bd2e5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F042546_39b9aaed43cdd2a1769203f852bd2e5a.png&h=9d531692&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"c92013e15deeaf3f060b507409fff5bc77c87536","tid":630081,"uid":138981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">fnn琴晚上水講述分身被BAN 自認肩狗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/010230_27141f160f3725886e099faf521974f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F010230_27141f160f3725886e099faf521974f7.png&h=fe8cad1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uplo